
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-richardson-6tisch-roll-join-priority-00.txt'>
    <title>"Enabling secure network join in RPL networks", Michael Richardson</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-richardson-6tisch-roll-join-priority-00.txt</link>
    <description>[I-D.richardson-6tisch-join-enhanced-beacon] defines a method by which a potential [I-D.ietf-6tisch-minimal-security] can announce itself as a available for new Pledges to Join a network.  The announcement includes a priority for join.  This document provides a mechanism by which a RPL DODAG root can disable join announcements, or adjust the base priority for join operation.</description>
    <dc:date>2017-07-18T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
